            "text": {
                "header": "The IPAW Laws",
                "body": "<p>There are no actual laws for IPAW. But if you want your plan's pricing to auto-approve, you'll need to make sure that it's following three rules. </p><p>Click on each rule to find out more about the IPAW rules.</p>",
                "class": "align-center-wide"
            },
            "interaction": {
                "name": "cr_ipaw2_s1",
                "id": "cr-ipaw2-s1",
                "type": "clickReveal",
                "items": [
                    {
                        "header": "Rule Number 1",
                        "body": "<p>Keep the average of all non-$0 lines, including flighted lines, greater than $500.</p>"
                    },
                    {
                        "header": "Rule Number 2",
                        "body": "<p>The CPM rates for some line items can be below the discount threshold. That's as long as other CPM rates make up the difference in revenue.</p>"
                    },
                    {
                        "header": "Rule Number 3",
                        "body": "<p>Some CPPs can be below the SQAD range Gross CPP Low, as long as other CPPs make up the difference in revenue. </p>"
                    }
                ]
            },
